{"tid":1677590,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"四色地圖定理的簡單展現","createTime":"2019-10-27T07:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T12:39:57.000Z","uid":64694,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"37ca88d42e6b0a1f0950b7690a3674aff13af230","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kuJxu5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkuJxu5c.png&h=f80a47ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n首先1d方面，可以用2種顏色就夠掂<br />\n<br />\n變成2d嘅話，首先由於要跨越2種顏色，所以需要第3種顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKyEUw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKyEUw9.png&h=f8fcaedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後如果變成咁應該點做呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aidJBN7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaidJBN7.png&h=ac33415f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最簡單嘅方法係直接用第4種顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPryY1y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPryY1y.png&h=b4ce4805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係其實諗深一層，暫時唔需要用到第4種顏色，只要將嗰3隻顏色調吓位就得喇，用嘅顏色愈少愈好，物盡其用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/af2yeA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faf2yeA7.png&h=9bb591e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後點解要第4種顏色呢？因為如果出面外圍有一層包住呢嚿嘢，邊位點都會有機會接觸到晒嗰3種顏色，所以需要第4隻色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWbLKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWbLKe.png&h=5b5ad26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果中間再斬開會點呢？唔通需要第5種顏色？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/we2FD4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwe2FD4m.png&h=ddd03457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔需要第5種顏色，只要調吓中間嚿嘢嘅顏色就得喇，可能有人會問之前咪調過，點解重可以調，因為之前調係基於只有3種顏色，而家可以用多一種，所以可以咁做，咁應該點調呢？<br />\n首先我哋可以見到中間條線只會穿過最上嘅綠色同埋最下嘅藍色，冇穿過黃色，所以只要將右手面嘅大型橙色格同所有喺右手邊大型橙色格入面嘅小型黃色格嘅顏色調轉就得喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PnK1oyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPnK1oyW.png&h=7027f63b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d85870712c43e9bd5099df26853d6c8466d223e","tid":1677590,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T07:56:30.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2a220e73dcd8f819cb097e35dc0f7cb82360cf","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"總括嚟講，調顏色避開相同顏色相近相鄰，用四種顏色搞掂"},{"pid":"86de66ccd840b4a80ee80c89793857cc742bb010","tid":1677590,"uid":184509,"like":14,"dislike":32,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"冇人明你噏乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaede600a209f89666be32b6698696a54142dab6","tid":1677590,"uid":37912,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"729391ea07b9d86f3a15830c4f7066a4cff16fd3","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"86de66ccd840b4a80ee80c89793857cc742bb010","tid":1677590,"uid":184509,"like":14,"dislike":32,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"冇人明你噏乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:50:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，因為我瞓教嘅時候突然諗到呢樣嘢，所以冇乜特別諗點樣表達出嚟，所以睇得明就會睇明，睇唔明就會睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0014b3fc7b967dc83cb90f56713591debe703e1d","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"btw，我覺得總會有人睇得明同我個腦同步sync<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ba64522e43083f0f26c77f08f7394ee9536f70","tid":1677590,"uid":284127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ba38f402a8699f6064c5e4ea24e8008d55799d","tid":1677590,"uid":87999,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"個定理目標係咩<br />\n限制係咩<br />\n要講左先<br />\n<br />\n唔係d人唔知你搞咩"},{"pid":"8bebb35b60e82d5a3e33ed85905efa735ab61d2e","tid":1677590,"uid":25973,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"Google 下世界地圖最少可以用幾多隻顏色油哂<br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個好practical 既地圖印刷問題 好早有數學家提出左solution了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝你你書本中搵到同你sync到既前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65311148a442fe1e6ab002c1c6467836f07d5170","tid":1677590,"uid":25973,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"btw覺得樓主解得好易明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1f75281cc773c9bec418751dc9b797b4d887e6","tid":1677590,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f24eb50fa961fdd22acd7a1f2e277587ae6c4d0d","tid":1677590,"uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"好有日本人既精神<br />\n認真研究d無謂既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7665e92c5290d423c029f007ad59ac46a840d955","tid":1677590,"uid":4238,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"樓主講得幾易明其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申：本身識</span></span>"},{"pid":"1140480262e3ee121ef9b2e91009c348292547f7","tid":1677590,"uid":108674,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"37ca88d42e6b0a1f0950b7690a3674aff13af230","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kuJxu5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkuJxu5c.png&h=f80a47ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n首先1d方面，可以用2種顏色就夠掂<br />\n<br />\n變成2d嘅話，首先由於要跨越2種顏色，所以需要第3種顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKyEUw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKyEUw9.png&h=f8fcaedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後如果變成咁應該點做呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aidJBN7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaidJBN7.png&h=ac33415f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最簡單嘅方法係直接用第4種顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPryY1y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPryY1y.png&h=b4ce4805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係其實諗深一層，暫時唔需要用到第4種顏色，只要將嗰3隻顏色調吓位就得喇，用嘅顏色愈少愈好，物盡其用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/af2yeA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faf2yeA7.png&h=9bb591e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後點解要第4種顏色呢？因為如果出面外圍有一層包住呢嚿嘢，邊位點都會有機會接觸到晒嗰3種顏色，所以需要第4隻色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWbLKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWbLKe.png&h=5b5ad26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果中間再斬開會點呢？唔通需要第5種顏色？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/we2FD4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwe2FD4m.png&h=ddd03457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔需要第5種顏色，只要調吓中間嚿嘢嘅顏色就得喇，可能有人會問之前咪調過，點解重可以調，因為之前調係基於只有3種顏色，而家可以用多一種，所以可以咁做，咁應該點調呢？<br />\n首先我哋可以見到中間條線只會穿過最上嘅綠色同埋最下嘅藍色，冇穿過黃色，所以只要將右手面嘅大型橙色格同所有喺右手邊大型橙色格入面嘅小型黃色格嘅顏色調轉就得喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PnK1oyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPnK1oyW.png&h=7027f63b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得ok喎<br />\n解釋得幾好<br />\n雖然未去到rigorous proof<br />\n但係基本idea出曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fdebad904f930a88c254ee6b8ffc5be805e13b","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"稍後解釋3d版"},{"pid":"4e514ccdcef17bf45fee41bf2ec9522d98875e44","tid":1677590,"uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61fdebad904f930a88c254ee6b8ffc5be805e13b","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"稍後解釋3d版"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:00:51.000Z","msg":"有冇n dimension 版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160d5ca6099ebd062d7c499a183811c99a974e66","tid":1677590,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5c04f13a2fa982ad71c184a3ce2708af88ab67b5","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"4e514ccdcef17bf45fee41bf2ec9522d98875e44","tid":1677590,"uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61fdebad904f930a88c254ee6b8ffc5be805e13b","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"稍後解釋3d版"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:00:51.000Z","msg":"有冇n dimension 版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"3d圖真係好難畫，花咗啲時間終於畫完<br />\n<br />\n喺3d嚟講，基本上係冇四色定理，因為3d可以顏色使用上係冇上限的，有啲情況係會使用到N種顏色，以下係一個比較常見嘅例子情況<br />\n<br />\n首先望吓呢幅圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AErSEmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAErSEmw.png&h=0e301e29&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢幅圖有2個波，而每個波會伸出一條管想連去其他波波嘅管，上面幅圖係第一個例子，一個波有一條管，其中一個條件係波同管嘅顏色係同一隻色不能變，因為佢哋係一體不可分割的（試諗吓就好似2D地圖嘅其中一格咁，不過佢係3D形式嘅一嚿嘢），如果想分辨呢兩件物體，就需要2種顏色，所以一個填上藍色，一個填上紅色，試諗吓如果兩件嘢都用到同一隻色，你係分唔到佢哋邊個打邊個，好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J3PdoTY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3PdoTY.png&h=98530891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如是者，繼續畫，而家有3個波，而家每個波有2條管連去其他波嘅管<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WO9GCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WO9GCw.png&h=befd8511&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n需要3種顏色<br />\n<br />\n之後而家有4個波，每個波有3條管連去其他波嘅管<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh85Zpx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh85Zpx.png&h=d50ef9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n需要4種顏色， 呢度要注意中間個交叉位，其實佢哋唔係4條黐埋一齊，而係紅黃連住，藍綠連住，紅黃條管喺藍綠上面，其實就係現實之中拎2條繩交叉疊住咁，因為3d所以要自己想像一下<br />\n<br />\n之後而家有5個波，每個波有4條管連去其他波嘅管<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CK5stkL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCK5stkL.png&h=fb53d83b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n需要5種顏色<br />\n<br />\n如果將其中一種顏色整走變4種顏色，最後點都會同其中一個波嘅顏色相同，因為同其中一個波顏色相同，所以佢條管會同另一個波條管撞色，所以分辨唔到佢兩個<br />\n好似話將橙變黃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ekDtXjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FekDtXjy.png&h=6468d2bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n或者將橙變紅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3X0strj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3X0strj.png&h=bf284981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n類此類推，6個波5條管需要6種顏色，7個波6條管需要7種顏色，N個波N-1條管需要N種顏色<br />\n<br />\n所以根據上面嘅情況，結論係，3D形式嘅地圖冇一個固定嘅最小著色數上限"},{"pid":"109af9e56503e2593490f1f78cdf2dde53374174","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"其實3d版本重有一個簡單啲嘅例子，可以容易啲諗到，其實可以諗吓有七條繩，如果呢7條繩係平排嘅話，只要好似1d咁用2種顏色就可以，但係如果將7條繩一齊扭埋一齊，咁嘅話入面每條繩都會接觸晒其他六條，所以要七種顏色先可以分辨，其實情景就好似上面個例子咁，只不過提供另一個諗法而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e5f94828fc9c3d916b4d1eca1b214de4cb704e","tid":1677590,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"勁，學習了"},{"pid":"12120d0102818ff21ad3e20d3093d9038d9a3cf4","tid":1677590,"uid":28