波，而家每個波有2條管連去其他波嘅管<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WO9GCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WO9GCw.png&h=befd8511&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n需要3種顏色<br />\n<br />\n之後而家有4個波，每個波有3條管連去其他波嘅管<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh85Zpx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh85Zpx.png&h=d50ef9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n需要4種顏色， 呢度要注意中間個交叉位，其實佢哋唔係4條黐埋一齊，而係紅黃連住，藍綠連住，紅黃條管喺藍綠上面，其實就係現實之中拎2條繩交叉疊住咁，因為3d所以要自己想像一下<br />\n<br />\n之後而家有5個波，每個波有4條管連去其他波嘅管<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CK5stkL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCK5stkL.png&h=fb53d83b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n需要5種顏色<br />\n<br />\n如果將其中一種顏色整走變4種顏色，最後點都會同其中一個波嘅顏色相同，因為同其中一個波顏色相同，所以佢條管會同另一個波條管撞色，所以分辨唔到佢兩個<br />\n好似話將橙變黃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ekDtXjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FekDtXjy.png&h=6468d2bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n或者將橙變紅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3X0strj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3X0strj.png&h=bf284981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n類此類推，6個波5條管需要6種顏色，7個波6條管需要7種顏色，N個波N-1條管需要N種顏色<br />\n<br />\n所以根據上面嘅情況，結論係，3D形式嘅地圖冇一個固定嘅最小著色數上限"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7906146e5a41ccf127b89265788dd472ecfd6575","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"話說3d嗰度有少少想補充返<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一個條件係波同同佢連接條管嘅顏色係同一隻色不能變，因為佢哋係一體不可分割的（試諗吓就好似2D地圖嘅其中一格咁，不過佢係3D形式嘅一嚿嘢）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢句嘢即係話波同佢連接嘅管係一嚿嘢嚟，好似下面咁波同條管係唔會分開的，而且一旦個波係藍色，佢連住嘅所有管都一定會係藍色，如果個波紅色，佢連住嘅所有管都一定會係紅色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yxv8kD0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxv8kD0.png&h=37e3574e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住想畫返4個波交叉嗰度，其實畫得好啲嘅可以唔需要畫到咁貼，畫得唔係幾好咁，其實可以畫到分開啲，好似咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVXiJnM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVXiJnM.jpg&h=2c521f70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LjyYJnM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjyYJnM.jpg&h=1fef2cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYYNBHN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYYNBHN.jpg&h=0087af42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ocOk9s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ocOk9s.jpg&h=5d713cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以睇吓唔同角度"},{"pid":"586189bab97109829b9ee43ec03909e53fe58443","tid":1677590,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c410a376b713947ddaa925f297a3cc7a058c2541","tid":1677590,"uid":42740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f24eb50fa961fdd22acd7a1f2e277587ae6c4d0d","tid":1677590,"uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"好有日本人既精神<br />\n認真研究d無謂既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"全部數學問題都好似好無謂"},{"pid":"f298b16a460efb3f3dd89817cf878538a93a504c","tid":1677590,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"前排好似有comment提過呢個原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3e5aea6db27e7ffb30861817370fb22a51d7ac","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"12120d0102818ff21ad3e20d3093d9038d9a3cf4","tid":1677590,"uid":286700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"有埋3d圖 勁<br />\n樓主係咪做researcch?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"唔係，瞓瞓吓教諗起呢樣嘢，唔知點解成日沖涼同瞓教嗰陣個腦就會諗到啲平日諗唔通嘅嘢，諗通咗之後就想用啲容易啲嘅諗法寫返低去解釋返畀自己聽，等之後唔記得嘅時候再睇返，就會容易啲明白返原來成件事係咁，因為有時候睇到人哋啲解釋啲字密麻麻咁又多公式可能要睇一段時間先知原來係咁，但係用圖像化嘅解釋可能會容易令人一睇就知係咁，即刻喺個腦有畫面，get到個idea同concept之後再睇返段原本解釋就會容易啲同快啲接受到明白到個意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知咁樣算唔算係好怪咁呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b742ea50e48adabe90e4c1521a9e8df2b90709fe","tid":1677590,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"學術post留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7619583334caef2ba6aa111478e19102999680b","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"btw，有冇人好似我咁成日瞓覺嘅時候個腦就會自動諗嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時會諗啲無謂嘢，有時會諗啲問題咁，有時又會諗到啲平時冇乜諗過嘅嘢，突如其來有idea，唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb88307f866de3a0ab37e326e38eb21d8f0fe62","tid":1677590,"uid":89064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24eb50fa961fdd22acd7a1f2e277587ae6c4d0d","tid":1677590,"uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"好有日本人既精神<br />\n認真研究d無謂既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"冇前人研究d無聊野，而家科技唔會咁進步。"},{"pid":"371cba771d227a6fff5d7cb66b37a72861f6f152","tid":1677590,"uid":22488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"仆街 <br />\n係關於咩架<br />\n張張圖都明但唔明想表達咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fc21170c7b626db5242dff2ed47903ef6cff9a","tid":1677590,"uid":32067