lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"簡單啲嚟講就係2d平面地圖上面，每一格自己同佢周圍嘅格嘅顏色都唔可以撞色，而只要4種顏色就可以做到呢樣嘢，任何2d地圖都得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"明哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有3D圖好有心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"但係3d就唔可以只用4隻色搞掂，只限於2d地圖，3d就如上面咁所講咁，有機會需要無限隻顏色先得，視乎個3d地圖係點而決定"},{"pid":"bd3aab6ca8957e9e80fd0961a221948292304a0a","tid":1677590,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSKH950.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSKH950.png&h=0771c7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJvHqEm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJvHqEm.png&h=b90dd842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">網上購買</span></strong><br />\nRoyal British Legion<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.poppyshop.org.uk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poppyshop.org.uk%2F&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=fe346b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.poppyshop.org.uk/</a><br />\n<br />\nM&amp;S Online<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marksandspencer.com/hk/search?q=Poppy&amp;lang=en_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marksandspencer.com%2Fhk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DPoppy%26lang%3Den_HK&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=4b6b96c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.marksandspencer.com/hk/search?q=Poppy&amp;lang=en_HK</a>"},{"pid":"2e715ab5dc5106c41a44e8db2cbeba1611df5692","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kuJxu5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkuJxu5c.png&h=f80a47ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n首先1d方面，可以用2種顏色就<span style=\"color: red;\">搞</span>掂<br />\n<br />\n變成2d嘅話，首先由於要跨越2種顏色，所以需要第3種顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKyEUw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKyEUw9.png&h=f8fcaedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後如果變成咁應該點做呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aidJBN7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaidJBN7.png&h=ac33415f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最簡單嘅方法係直接用第4種顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPryY1y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPryY1y.png&h=b4ce4805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係其實諗深一層，暫時唔需要用到第4種顏色，只要將嗰3隻顏色調吓位就得喇，用嘅顏色<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量</span>愈少愈好，物盡其用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/af2yeA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faf2yeA7.png&h=9bb591e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後點解要第4種顏色呢？因為如果出面外圍有一層包住呢嚿嘢，邊位點都會有機會接觸到晒嗰3種顏色，所以需要第4隻色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWbLKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWbLKe.png&h=5b5ad26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果中間再斬開會點呢？唔通需要第5種顏色？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/we2FD4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwe2FD4m.png&h=ddd03457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔需要第5種顏色，只要調吓中間嚿嘢嘅顏色就得喇，可能有人會問之前咪調過，點解重可以調，因為之前調係基於只有3種顏色，而家可以用多一種，所以可以咁做，咁應該點調呢？<br />\n首先我哋可以見到中間條線只<span style=\"color: red;\">係掂到</span>最上嘅綠色同埋最下嘅藍色，冇<span style=\"color: red;\">掂到</span>黃色，所以只要將右手面嘅大型橙色格同所有喺右手邊大型橙色格入面嘅小型黃色格嘅顏色<span style=\"color: red;\">倒轉swap</span>就得喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PnK1oyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPnK1oyW.png&h=7027f63b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2116e68364a213bd6045e1db627df85b8dd72bac","tid":1677590,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"想要PROOF <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6220365c93ad999b793bfb978c8027d3d22ca63","tid":1677590,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"Ching讀數？"},{"pid":"eb78cd9dd672fd8dba569e830443daa27ee703c3","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"3d方面，又有另一個例子<br />\n假設有7條L字型嘅物體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FyxVxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FyxVxB.jpg&h=7209af2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後將佢哋咁疊埋一齊，就需要7種顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AV2e8SL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAV2e8SL.jpg&h=b73fb0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果得6種顏色，例如將3號L物體轉為紅色，就會同1號L物體撞色，因為同為紅色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VZttSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VZttSW.jpg&h=dcec62e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論係如果再多啲L物體繼續排落去，有N條L物體就需要N種顏色先可以令咁多條L物體唔會因此而撞色，所以3D形式嘅地圖冇一個固定嘅最小著色數上限"},{"pid":"d47e4792bbddf97c2c7a619ad8b22233fe1dea35","tid":1677590,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86de66ccd840b4a80ee80c89793857cc742bb010","tid":1677590,"uid":184509,"like":14,"dislike":32,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"冇人明你噏乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"細個有冇睇神探伽利略架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13682af625af2e6209f5c68c25b58d7941e63361","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6220365c93ad999b793bfb978c8027d3d22ca63","tid":1677590,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"Ching讀數？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"唔係，但有時會留意吓睇吓呢啲得意有趣嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d4931d20c2df9775e6595545271e8e61abc3aa","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:13:56.000Z","msg":"btw，另外我寫呢篇嘢嘅原因係想用最簡單易明嘅方式去講解呢個問題，令人容易啲入手，我想嘗試用最簡單嘅例子開始去簡介，之後再逐步深入，層層遞進<br />\n<br />\n好似話由1d開始到2d，再由2d到3d，感覺好似有少少引人入局咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我覺得呢種方式嘅好處係唔使一嚟就講啲好難嘅嘢去嚇怕人唔敢接觸，反而係首先用一個簡單嘅方式去講解令人容易啲接受，令人覺得有趣吸引人去諗呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3680eb91f9ed27cff0ba70e7b8c9838464a044","tid":1677590,"uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"簡單嚟講就係我想做到「由淺入深」四個字，一開頭用有趣講法嘅introduction引人入局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，唔知有冇人睇幪面超人build呢？<br />\n其實幪面超人build每一集個標題都用咗唔同嘅公式，而第4集嘅公式就係呢個「四色地圖定理」喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjtqC5C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjtqC5C.jpg&h=16fd6e5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91bc1432294ad7c1737bcde73a88a353d86b793d","tid":1677590,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"Graph theory<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d344c6317c071ab02f51c4f8122ecebe32961f41","tid":1677590,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}